{
  "id": "RAW_a2a235f2",
  "title": "成本暴降 99%！万人大会系统全是 AI 生成的，Vibe Coding 真上战场了",
  "url": "https://www.qbitai.com/2025/11/353556.html",
  "date": "2025-11-17 12:28:12",
  "author": "西风",
  "siteName": "量子位",
  "content": "<!--摘要样式-->\n<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-forward-slash\" data-track=\"83\">西风 发自 凹非寺</p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-forward-slash\" data-track=\"84\">量子位 | 公众号 QbitAI</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"2\">你敢信，国内大厂的万人年度大会，从邀请函、官网到留资、参会、签到、现场活动的<strong>整套系统由AI凭几句话生成</strong>，智能体正在从“可玩”走向“可用”。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"3\">没错，就是下面这一整套：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/1f0cb2b1c0dbcd90b8e4441c0414df85.gif\" data-src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/1f0cb2b1c0dbcd90b8e4441c0414df85.gif\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"4\">靠几句大白话驱使AI搞定，程序员只负责坐等结果：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/6359df97f66ebdbbf8ab2df471aa5148.gif\" data-src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/6359df97f66ebdbbf8ab2df471aa5148.gif\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"5\">过去大家还把这种工具当个“玩具”随便试试，谁能想到，现在它已经能扛起企业级的正儿八经业务了。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"6\">在刚刚结束的百度世界大会2025上，<strong>无代码对话式应用搭建平台——“秒哒”，宣布进化到2.0</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"7\">相比上一代，2.0有两大升级点：</p>\n  <ul>\n   <li data-track=\"8\"><strong>全栈应用一键生成</strong>：把做应用的开发、调试、线上部署等整套环节全包了。</li>\n   <li data-track=\"9\"><strong>一站式开发与分发</strong>：由秒哒打造的应用可一键发布到公网，同时能打通搜索引擎得到曝光，支持发布成微信小程序。</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-track=\"10\">基于这套能力，大会全链路系统就是它从0到1吭哧吭哧建出来的。据估算，相比传统纯人工开发，其综合<strong>成本暴降99%</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"11\">更有意思的是，会上百度秒哒产品负责人还跟观众了进行现场互动，同样是一行代码不写，当场构建了一个个人闲置物品电商平台。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"12\">这不是个只靠好看界面撑场子的展示品，而是个<strong>前后端逻辑、数据库、AI试衣插件、支付能力全都配齐的完整应用</strong>，可以直接上线，还能接入搜索引擎，真正把一个小店铺给支棱起来。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/1afab065d99b767a5e1fd9f3c7c4d6a5.gif\" data-src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/1afab065d99b767a5e1fd9f3c7c4d6a5.gif\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"13\">商家能在后台上架商品、管理数据：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/2cdba2f9505a4f23074acd191e5fd3e6.gif\" data-src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/2cdba2f9505a4f23074acd191e5fd3e6.gif\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"14\">买家能线上选购、上传照片AI试衣：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251117131027_1a65838b7303e0e724d5198cd48cde1a.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251117131027_1a65838b7303e0e724d5198cd48cde1a.png\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"15\">还能真实填写地址提交订单：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/af5419146a35d381ba34379a12c4433b.gif\" data-src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/af5419146a35d381ba34379a12c4433b.gif\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"16\">现场演示真刀真枪跑完了支付流程，台下观众甚至有人抢在官方前头，抢先一步扫码把订单付了。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251117131027_f4ecb6e656c2b960e4121d2b06967ccf.gif\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251117131027_f4ecb6e656c2b960e4121d2b06967ccf.gif\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"17\">well～well～well</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251117131027_22576eb8ab314273f29f1b2dc218e412.gif\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251117131027_22576eb8ab314273f29f1b2dc218e412.gif\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"18\">既然如此，量子位童鞋立马上手体验了一波。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"20\">打开官网，能看到主页应用广场中有大量应用已经在公网上线了。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p26-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/16447cdea479466badef839de5ca7951~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=ThamqhicoUSA8uiVjME7aX5NU2U%3D\" data-src=\"https://p26-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/16447cdea479466badef839de5ca7951~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=ThamqhicoUSA8uiVjME7aX5NU2U%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"21\">购物类网站品类清晰，支持折扣标价、购物车结算、用户登录等完整功能：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/e207f2f7df154e298c81073ea0f507b6~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=iH6DTTcc1YExozn8vgnHOM4lWh4%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/e207f2f7df154e298c81073ea0f507b6~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=iH6DTTcc1YExozn8vgnHOM4lWh4%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"22\">还有Nano Banana 3D手办工坊，自带JS前端特效，交互流畅无卡顿。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a3d3b36374044fbd83a7e9fa6765c4ee~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=JWKCPzFmyukf0pcexH0CwbbWmvA%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a3d3b36374044fbd83a7e9fa6765c4ee~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=JWKCPzFmyukf0pcexH0CwbbWmvA%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"23\">随手就能生成“高雅人士企鹅”系列盲盒：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/1c1c995f868442a99cffa42bf118701d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=2IaMA%2Ft3mLKxrgJNdd4yk5X8mJ4%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/1c1c995f868442a99cffa42bf118701d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=2IaMA%2Ft3mLKxrgJNdd4yk5X8mJ4%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"24\">下面以搭建一个“北京小猫小狗领养平台”为例，记录一下完整开发过程。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"25\">首先输入端，支持上传文件、图片辅助描述的同时，还能让<strong>AI自动优化指令</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"26\">不得不说，这个AI自动优化确实有点东西，它能<strong>把一句笼统的话，自动补充成一份考虑周全的需求说明</strong>，瞬间就让你的想法变得像样起来，这下就算需求模糊不会表达也不怕了：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/9034cc7068f5402392c2b9c95e1380e2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=bUDKuLAAGXGGOr4RyEiYrxuiC78%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/9034cc7068f5402392c2b9c95e1380e2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=bUDKuLAAGXGGOr4RyEiYrxuiC78%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"27\">另外，如果你要做微信小程序，可以直接点击输入框下面的对应按钮。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"28\">微信支付、图像编辑、视频生成、语音生成等<strong>一系列插件也都有配备，选用即可，无需额外开发对接</strong>：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/3573db408e6b4d9ea8965c477a3994e5~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=3drLhljCbbsBW4uN5yHl9QoPNuE%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/3573db408e6b4d9ea8965c477a3994e5~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=3drLhljCbbsBW4uN5yHl9QoPNuE%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"29\">接下来，秒哒会先<strong>根据用户指令整理一份详细的需求文档</strong>，支持编辑修改：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/db26cfd5ce7e41a890642db7314ff97b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=IMBWhEUR8P717MkgrHMprWNIjAc%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/db26cfd5ce7e41a890642db7314ff97b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=IMBWhEUR8P717MkgrHMprWNIjAc%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"30\">确认无误后点击“立即生成应用”，自动编码正式启动：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/14e1d6bea58542ac99a17ccec081a210~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=XNYFxHjrJx36v0oQH4LO1kqq2Pc%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/14e1d6bea58542ac99a17ccec081a210~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=XNYFxHjrJx36v0oQH4LO1kqq2Pc%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"31\">稍等片刻，一个宠物领养网站就出炉了。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"32\">令人眼前一亮的是，秒哒第一次生成就成功了。按照指令设置，它已经预先生成上传了一批宠物身份卡，还按猫咪、狗狗分好类：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/62ffd09086594eccb85ebcae85329a91~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=9evtPrh7akgaInF%2Bs8J2Lo%2FvUEc%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/62ffd09086594eccb85ebcae85329a91~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=9evtPrh7akgaInF%2Bs8J2Lo%2FvUEc%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"33\">传统无代码平台，大多擅长快速构建前端用户界面，但一到复杂的后端业务逻辑、数据库设计和接口联调，往往仍需专业开发者介入。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"34\">而这个由秒哒一键开发的宠物领养平台，管理员登录后就能实现后台管理。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/0e550599fdb44b7fa917f0f775f7f6b6~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=OTYTnlGzDFQ0ClvhooluHSP99Lg%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/0e550599fdb44b7fa917f0f775f7f6b6~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=OTYTnlGzDFQ0ClvhooluHSP99Lg%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"35\">每只宠物的信息都能编辑，若被领养，也能实时更新状态：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/ee4fdf3f174e4c21a06ff250843612e4~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=UpI2wZYv79gE3olbgodQFmVTP2c%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/ee4fdf3f174e4c21a06ff250843612e4~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=UpI2wZYv79gE3olbgodQFmVTP2c%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"36\">除此之外，娱乐场景咱也试试。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"37\">接下来我们用它快速创建“<strong>狗了个狗</strong>”小游戏：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p26-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/12a4b5148a6a41098c59c23fd27a3864~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=lZ%2FWYpRxZJLttXou%2Fo2Qas%2BdLn4%3D\" data-src=\"https://p26-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/12a4b5148a6a41098c59c23fd27a3864~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=lZ%2FWYpRxZJLttXou%2Fo2Qas%2BdLn4%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"38\">同样几分钟后，咱已经上手玩上了：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/4ffdaa3bd69f485082f9e2136b729bb2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=9enEn7qnvqJ6YwFpDaEk51Q0x6Y%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/4ffdaa3bd69f485082f9e2136b729bb2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=9enEn7qnvqJ6YwFpDaEk51Q0x6Y%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"39\">再来模仿小破站搭建一个简易视频网站：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/9c51c627a2c041ba9a72c082abaef0e6~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=ThNCceYh8SjBDkAHTm%2BFBojtAdw%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/9c51c627a2c041ba9a72c082abaef0e6~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=ThNCceYh8SjBDkAHTm%2BFBojtAdw%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"40\">也完全可以在登录后，顺利上传发布视频：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/bc7cc249a1db48c08df56e9d0bf59df8~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=9t%2F5baLX3hV0kZuD1dnFpzoZCdc%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/bc7cc249a1db48c08df56e9d0bf59df8~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=9t%2F5baLX3hV0kZuD1dnFpzoZCdc%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"41\">弹幕、评论、点赞等核心功能都是打开即可正常使用：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/246af08abab54d3fb6edd9c3fdffde9a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=wSqoIjYTwRPZTJhXQoGpQhxPkqU%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/246af08abab54d3fb6edd9c3fdffde9a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=wSqoIjYTwRPZTJhXQoGpQhxPkqU%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"42\">有任何不满意的地方，也只需一句话让它给你修改。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"43\">最后，这些生成的应用皆可一键发布。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"44\">域名和证书配置完成后便能立即上线，并且与搜索引擎贯通，可获得面向亿级用户的曝光入口。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/815817562b9e478ea6ef9672e1289ed4~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=pTryEK4YUwtiFDdAVrf5O4gvtyQ%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/815817562b9e478ea6ef9672e1289ed4~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=pTryEK4YUwtiFDdAVrf5O4gvtyQ%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"45\">如果你有好的想法，不妨亲自上手试试。没有想法的话，那再来看两个例子，或许能给你一点启发。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"46\">有人用它搭起了能实际运营的<strong>表情包社区</strong>，用户可以为自己喜欢的表情包付费，所有内容和用户数据都能在后台统一管理：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/5321ee8013554c30835acec644075d00~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=egvukMFbwO3dDktyT4%2FHQEpsNDI%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/5321ee8013554c30835acec644075d00~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=egvukMFbwO3dDktyT4%2FHQEpsNDI%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"47\">还有人做了个“<strong>双十一凑单计算助手</strong>”，只要输入商品价格、选好优惠券，就能帮你算出最划算的购买方案：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/30e4cee695484fb2978ca007717062de~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=s%2B5lTL59NOc8ILTAk12HjkjqeQQ%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/30e4cee695484fb2978ca007717062de~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=s%2B5lTL59NOc8ILTAk12HjkjqeQQ%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"48\">下面问题来了，如此流畅完整的应用生成体验，是怎么做到的？</p>\n  <p data-track=\"50\">从尝鲜小玩具进化为能扛住复杂场景、高标准要求的商业级工具，秒哒2.0的核心解法也不藏了——</p>\n  <p data-track=\"51\"><strong>多智能体协作</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"52\">当用户输入一段自然语言需求后，平台内部并非单一模型在响应，而是由一个智能体团队在协同工作：</p>\n  <p data-track=\"53\">产品经理智能体负责梳理需求，架构师智能体设计技术方案，程序员智能体负责前后端编码，测试员智能体则保障应用质量……</p>\n  <p data-track=\"54\">这套分工机制，模拟了一个微型开发团队的完整流程，从而能够输出一个全栈应用。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"55\">而要让这个应用能真的好用起来的，还离不开两大关键支撑。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"56\">一方面是<strong>百度生态的深度整合</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"57\">背靠百度智能云，秒哒生成应用时能直接调用百度的各种成熟工具，不用你自己找接口、做复杂对接。比如想在邀请函里加会场定位，就能自动调用百度地图插件；报名环节需要验证码，短信服务直接启用，语音、搜索这些功能也能一键激活。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"58\">甚至支付、域名购买这些商业相关的功能，在平台上就能一站式搞定，百度本身也就具备域名管理与售卖能力。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"59\">换句话说，<strong>一个个人应用从诞生的那一刻起，就天然具备了接入商业世界各种服务的能力</strong>。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p26-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/d38025457e894ef8840ae7dac1c1daf2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=qi82O%2BmSsBuGIGieU22y7Johq9g%3D\" data-src=\"https://p26-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/d38025457e894ef8840ae7dac1c1daf2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=qi82O%2BmSsBuGIGieU22y7Johq9g%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"60\">另一方面是<strong>后端能力的持续升级</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"61\">早期秒哒只能做静态展示，就像简单的网页一样。随着不断升级，现在生成应用时会自动配好数据库，不用你自己注册、设置任何参数，上传的内容、提交的订单都会安全存储，后续想查数据、改内容，在后台就能直接操作，支持增删改查，完全满足长期使用需求。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"62\">总结来看，从应用开发到上线再到触达用户，在秒哒上可以实现全程无缝衔接。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"63\">这套技术体系也得到了权威认可，根据IDC发布的《中国无代码生成式应用开发平台实测报告2025》，<strong>秒哒总体能力行业领先</strong>：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/f6b300657dbd4b6f83f1586ac3e9af38~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=FUe%2F1hAS9vYSuTaagOMtuv5qn9M%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/f6b300657dbd4b6f83f1586ac3e9af38~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=FUe%2F1hAS9vYSuTaagOMtuv5qn9M%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"64\">尤其是在服务集成、用户与生态、应用类型支持、应用复杂度支持、功能完整性等方面表现突出：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/fb8dd9f904744b92af0c8c22214e71f9~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=5PzP2cRi40jBQxVOW%2B7HdbpxOlM%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/fb8dd9f904744b92af0c8c22214e71f9~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=5PzP2cRi40jBQxVOW%2B7HdbpxOlM%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"66\">官方数据显示，秒哒平台上，<strong>至今已诞生了超过40万个应用</strong>，平均每分钟就有一个新应用诞生。这些应用覆盖教育、电商、办公、企业管理等场景。AI驱动的应用开发，正在从演示层走向真实复杂的日常业务环境。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"67\">如此体量应用的背后，是过去始终被高技术门槛所压抑的海量个性化、长尾化的需求。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"68\">放眼全球，真会写代码的人不足1%，而秒哒这类工具，让剩下的99%的人，无论背景、无论年龄，都能把自己的想法转化为真实可用的数字产品。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"69\">为了鼓励更多人能把脑洞变成产品，百度秒哒还跟小红书科技一拍即合，联合发起了<strong>中国首届非程序员黑客松大赛</strong>，把全球不会敲代码、但脑洞突破天际的人都薅了过来。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/ec4a122b481f4f2f9c811bddcb4b7512~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=qYuuUCtVhAQUEcxzsRkgFV%2BlLAY%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/ec4a122b481f4f2f9c811bddcb4b7512~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=qYuuUCtVhAQUEcxzsRkgFV%2BlLAY%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"70\">在黑客松大赛中，我们看到作品<strong>《技能五子棋》</strong>，凭借出色的可玩性和高度还原的游戏体验，成功闯入决赛：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/38702db9ea0e47a6a56a86599e396bd9~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=Zo8M7IgzX8tF55UW0deDiBFCs58%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/38702db9ea0e47a6a56a86599e396bd9~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=Zo8M7IgzX8tF55UW0deDiBFCs58%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"71\">作品<strong>《化学分子结构分析》</strong>则让我们看到了另一种学习方式。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"72\">输入化学分子式，点击一键分析，就能立马查看其3D结构：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/cb36a431993f45b7a3d66b7fd53a7fc6~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=PthlPqAnmbyCyhBmbDHZcoJp5ZY%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/cb36a431993f45b7a3d66b7fd53a7fc6~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=PthlPqAnmbyCyhBmbDHZcoJp5ZY%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"73\">更进一步，路易斯结构式、电子结构分析、化学键参数分析、原子轨道电子排布分析等等一应俱全：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img syl-img-loading\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/d20326ced8764298920adad939b4b985~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=%2FxA0YNWvK3Vsfvgkubs870iThG0%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/d20326ced8764298920adad939b4b985~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=%2FxA0YNWvK3Vsfvgkubs870iThG0%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"74\">随着以秒哒2.0为代表的AI开发工具能力持续升级，当由AI开发的应用不断被注入更稳固的后端能力、更强大的逻辑处理和完善的生态服务，创意也不再止于好玩了。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"75\">个性化教育工具、垂直领域专业应用、社交娱乐产品……条条大路通商业化。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"76\">事实上，在技术社区中已经可以看到一些探索方向。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"77\">WaytoAGI社区负责人最近就表示，他们尤其看好秒哒在构建<strong>聚合类内容平台、SVG设计工具、可视化仪表盘及媒体生成工具</strong>等垂直应用方面的潜力。</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-track=\"78\">我们最近通过深挖细分行业的长尾关键词，锁定了一个精准场景。我在想，如果把这个场景单独提炼出来，用秒哒批量化生成对应的应用，再嵌入一些付费功能，或许能探索出全新的商业化方向。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"79\">从秒哒官方公布的数据来看，平台上诞生的应用也呈现出明显的场景化特征，<strong>大量应用都集中于解决某个垂直且具体的实际问题</strong>：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/93f0f00f6bb34c988598c09b2a3725c2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=vKpduDMdxnP1s6HHCALZ1OR3Q1I%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/93f0f00f6bb34c988598c09b2a3725c2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=vKpduDMdxnP1s6HHCALZ1OR3Q1I%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"80\">值得一提的是，世界另一边，<strong>秒哒海外版MeDo也已上线</strong>，还曾一度登上全球科技新品发现与推广社区Product Hunt的产品日榜榜首，歪果仁一样用得津津有味，现在访问medo.dev就可以使用了。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/67e7d44188434878a91021fd0ed19814~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=ilowHbUPWyfQ80gsX8%2FmHjuAt5Q%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/67e7d44188434878a91021fd0ed19814~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251117202751F409D6FCE6FFB4200A75&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=ilowHbUPWyfQ80gsX8%2FmHjuAt5Q%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"81\">也许未来最难的，不是写代码，而是想清楚你想让AI帮你做什么。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"85\">官方体验链接：https://www.miaoda.cn/</p>\n  <!--版权声明-->\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "AI 驱动的百度“秒哒 2.0”实现全栈应用对话式生成，成本暴降 99%，赋能非程序员快速构建复杂商业应用。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "AI 驱动的百度“秒哒 2.0”实现全栈应用对话式生成，成本暴降 99%，赋能非程序员快速构建复杂商业应用。",
  "summary": "文章深入介绍了百度“秒哒 2.0”无代码对话式应用搭建平台的显著升级。该平台通过 AI 凭自然语言指令，能够实现从邀请函、官网到签到等万人大会全链路系统的全栈生成，相比传统人工开发，综合成本预估暴降 99%。秒哒 2.0 的核心升级点包括：实现全栈应用的一键生成，涵盖开发、调试、线上部署等环节；以及提供一站式开发与分发能力，支持应用发布到公网并打通搜索引擎，同时可生成微信小程序。文章通过现场演示构建闲置物品电商平台、宠物领养平台、小游戏和视频网站等多个案例，详细展示了秒哒 2.0 在前后端逻辑、数据库、AI 插件（如 AI 试衣）及支付能力方面的完整性。其技术核心在于多智能体协作机制，模拟产品经理、架构师、程序员、测试员等团队协同工作，并深度整合百度智能云生态服务，持续强化后端能力。根据 IDC 报告，秒哒总体能力行业领先，目前已诞生超过 40 万个应用，旨在降低技术门槛，赋能 99%的非程序员将创意转化为真实可用的数字产品。值得一提的是，其海外版 MeDo 已上线并曾登上 Product Hunt 日榜榜首，展现了其全球影响力。",
